{
    "text": "The vast Inle Lake is located in the Shan Mountains in central Burma. Near its southern tip, the multi-tiered Phaung Daw U pagoda is home to golden statues. In the hills that rise near the village of Indein, the stupas of the Shwe Indein pagoda look like a field of golden arrows. Not far away, the forest has taken over the stupas of Nyaung Ohak. At the northern end of the lake, a wooden bridge connects the floating village of Maing Thauk to the shore.   \"Fishermen of \u0130nle lake \" Those images look like a painting, right ?  #discoverburma\ud83c\uddf2\ud83c\uddf2 with @ilhan1077   . . . . . .  #burma  #myanmar  #bagan  #mandalay  #yangon  #lake  #reflection  #water  #boat  #lago  #natur  #irox_water  #ignaturale  #trees  #igcentric_nature  #est  #cloud  #onda",
